### Description

Script for installing OCServ v1.3.0 on clean Debian OS.

To install ocserv run:
```
bash <(curl -Ls https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LazyGatto/ocserv-debian/main/install-ocserv.sh)
```

You can modify default settings afterwards, ie listening ports
Dont forget to restart oscerv if so...
```
systemctl restart ocserv.service
```